                <head>217. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On June 20, 1961, Secretary <persName corresp="#p_RD3">Rusk</persName> held
                    several conversations with Japanese officials on a number of topics regarding
                    U.S.-Japanese relations. One of these conversations on liberalization of trade
                    and payments is scheduled for publication in <ref target="frus1961-63v22">volume
                        XXII</ref>.</p>
            </div>
